      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this beauty\u2014it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve pampered this car since day one, and it\u2019s in absolutely pristine shape. No scratches, no stories, just a smooth, perfect ride that's ready for its next home. If you want that brand-new feeling without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
