    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This specimen is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a precise 6-speed manual gearbox. The mechanical integrity is absolute: the dual-VANOS system has been bulletproofed, and the rear subframe has undergone proactive reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. The limited-slip differential operates silently, and the suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications with fresh OEM bushings throughout. The exterior retains its original deep-luster finish, while the interior Nappa leather shows zero bolster wear. This is a mechanically sorted, turn-key example for the purist seeking the pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
