    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, meticulously preserved to remain in showroom condition. The exterior features a deep, ceramic-coated luster entirely free of swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings, while the original alloy wheels show zero curb rash. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium upholstery is taut with no bolster wear, the carpets are pristine, and it retains a fresh, smoke-free scent. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the climate control, operates with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, backed by a complete, documented service history from authorized specialists. Always garage-kept under a breathable cover and never driven in rain, this is a rare, investment-grade example for the most discerning buyer.",
      "price": 48500.0,
